# [GRAIN] Phase 5A extension-registry SECRET keys — never commit. Only the
# PUBLIC keys (pinned in grain-core) and the signed seed docs are tracked. The
# `.key` files here are the development root/publishing secrets; the production
# ones move to encrypted removable media as the final migration step.
registry-keys/
*.key

